                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "De dire en le voyant : Je ne le connais point.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "Qu'y faire ? Ramener son manteau sur sa plaie,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "Et sous un rire faux cacher sa douleur vraie ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "Dévorer par orgueil les larmes de ses yeux,",
