                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 45,
                    "line_text": "Incapable à jamais d'un élan grandiose,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 46,
                    "line_text": "De toute sa hauteur descendre dans la prose,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 47,
                    "line_text": "Comme l'aigle blessé qui, sanglant, sur le sol",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 48,
                    "line_text": "Tombe, ne fermant pas la courbe de son vol.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 49,
                    "line_text": "Me défiant de moi, malade de l'absence,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 50,
                    "line_text": "Ne vivant qu'à demi, voilà ce que je pense :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 51,
                    "line_text": "Si tu ne m'aimais plus, oh ! ce serait ma mort ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 52,
                    "line_text": "Mais tu m'aimes toujours, n'est-ce pas, et j'ai tort.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 53,
                    "line_text": "Au lieu de tout cela, sans doute, jeune fille,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 54,
                    "line_text": "Rêveuse, de tes doigts laissant fuir ton aiguille,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 55,
                    "line_text": "Vers le chemin désert tu tournes tes grands yeux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
