                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 56,
                    "line_text": "Et, portant ta main blanche à ton front soucieux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 57,
                    "line_text": "Tu te dis en toi-même : Il ne vient pas, — tu pleures ;",
