                    "line_text": "Remontant le passé, voltige autour de toi ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 68,
                    "line_text": "Il te souffle à l'oreille une phrase de moi,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 69,
                    "line_text": "Un soupir, un serment, quelque mot tendre, et pose",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
